column5: I bring the suck!! That is all
Sounds like you did about as good as I did on the Beaver today
Oooooooooooo!... now there's an epic report!!!
Don't beat yourself up over it.... stuff like that happens to the best of us    I'm as guilty as any
There's always tomorrow, I went out at 7:20 and until 11:30 only had a few bumps, then put down the simple #8 hook, minnow and 2 splitshot on bottom..10 minutes..2 whities.

Cliff I can't believe that you haven't had any luck on lady simcoe.... they've been catching them left and right lol Like I said before, I'm as guilty as any  Will be waiting for your report!! Jacques
